# Scaffold-regler

Arkitektur: `docs/architecture/scaffold-system.md`.

## Canonical paths

| Sak | Path |
|---|---|
| Scaffold-filer | `src/lib/gen/scaffolds/<id>/files/` |
| Scaffold manifest | `src/lib/gen/scaffolds/<id>/manifest.ts` |
| Registry/types | `src/lib/gen/scaffolds/registry.ts`, `types.ts` |
| Variants | `config/scaffold-variants/<scaffold>/<variant>.json` |
| Variant schema | `docs/schemas/strict/scaffold-variant.schema.json` |

## Regler

1. Redigera scaffold-filer direkt i `files/`.
2. Metadata i `manifest.ts`.
3. Kör `npm run typecheck` + `npm run scaffolds:validate` efter ändringar.
4. Ändra inte `serialize.ts`, `registry.ts`, `seo-defaults.ts`, `finalize-merge.ts` eller `protected-paths.ts` utan att förstå merge-pipeline.
5. Externa referenser och research går via dossier-/reference-pipen, inte gamla template-library-script.
6. Innan ta bort/slå ihop scaffold: sök referenser, variantmappar, registry, embeddings och docs.

## Merge-policy

- `LLM_ONLY_PATHS`: scaffold-default blockas, LLM måste emittera.
- `SCAFFOLD_PROTECTED_PATHS`: LLM-emission droppas, scaffold/previous vinner.

Lägg bara rena utility-filer i protected paths.
